{"tid":634772,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple即將發明雙卡雙待iphone","createTime":"2018-04-19T14:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T10:45:18.000Z","uid":82587,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"65a3ee23025e161cafdde27c42e2926d39a3f0e9","tid":634772,"uid":82587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T14:10:49.000Z","msg":"Apple analyst Ming-Chi Kuo of KGI Securities has today issued a new investor note in which he offers up additional details on this year&rsquo;s iPhone refresh. This time, Kuo says the 6.1-inch LCD iPhone introduced this year could feature support for dual-SIM technology and be priced as low as $550&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nKuo&rsquo;s note explains that the 6.1-inch LCD iPhone could be available in two models: one with a standard single SIM setup and another with dual SIM dual standby, which could mean having two physical SIM card slots and no eSIM support.<br />\nKuo&rsquo;s report&nbsp;adds to an earlier Bloomberg report, which said that Apple was considering dual SIM technology for the 6.5-inch OLED iPhone. Kuo also corroborates dual SIM support for the 6.5-inch model in today&rsquo;s report and says it will not come to the 5.8-inch OLED variant.<br />\nAs for price, KGI says the new dual SIM iPhone could create another price segment for the iPhone. The analyst says the single SIM model could sell for between $550 and $650, while the dual SIM model would sell for between $650 and $750. Ultimately, Kuo says the single SIM model could &ldquo;help increase market share in China and commercial markets.&rdquo;<br />\nKuo remains bullish on sales of the 6.1-inch LCD iPhone, as well. He predicts Apple could sell between 100 million and 120 million units between the third quarter of 2018 and the third quarter of 2019.<br />\nKGI, Bloomberg, and others have offered details on the 2018 iPhone lineup thus far. Apple is&nbsp;said to have three new models in store, including a 5.8-inch iPhone X refresh, a brand new 6.1-inch LCD iPhone, and a 6.5-inch OLED &ldquo;iPhone X Plus.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"70cb5964e958899f9e42b0885e1479936b0b47f1","tid":634772,"uid":120859,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T14:42:46.000Z","msg":"iSim <br />\nSim id<br />\napple sim <br />\nthe sim<br />\nthe new sim <br />\nsim pro"},{"pid":"f2c818f6b159defb44eb513c3b612e3b5e749ccb","tid":634772,"uid":164092,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T14:44:02.000Z","msg":"發明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568ed8339c1b2f051cdd369926fc018c0661f6ef","tid":634772,"uid":82587,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f2c818f6b159defb44eb513c3b612e3b5e749ccb","tid":634772,"uid":164092,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T14:44:02.000Z","msg":"發明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T14:44:32.000Z","msg":"定發現!?"},{"pid":"09a0b3532c3d32d4510898018ef774c9345219f9","tid":634772,"uid":46835,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T15:05:17.000Z","msg":"嘩<br />\n點係呀....<br />\n咁都俾佢諗到, 勁呀 !!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc45da696978c472175e0554c33571cb6f7be824","tid":634772,"uid":3241,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T15:16:18.000Z","msg":"蘋果人活在井底嘛， 同發現新大陸一樣"},{"pid":"d73a812e4b6173f139cd11c5dacf94bd2e49b970","tid":634772,"uid":174418,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T15:28:54.000Z","msg":"點解係發明? 好多機都有雙卡啦"},{"pid":"1d65b4f1b5127d7954359a5cf2561c0cc5b8793c","tid":634772,"uid":82587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d73a812e4b6173f139cd11c5dacf94bd2e49b970","tid":634772,"uid":174418,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T15:28:54.000Z","msg":"點解係發明? 好多機都有雙卡啦"},"citedBy":1